Model 1: is_canceled ~ adrCent + adultsCent + season + changed + origin + 
    hotel + is_repeated_guest + lead_time_squared + market_segment + 
    prior_cancellation + length_stayCent + adrCent:season + season:lead_time_squared
Model 2: is_canceled ~ adrCent + adultsCent + season + changed + origin + 
    hotel + is_repeated_guest + lead_time_squared + market_segment + 
    prior_cancellation + length_stayCent + (season * adrCent) + 
    (season * lead_time_squared) + (adrCent * hotel)
